e = January 2014 |url = https://waterfordmi.gov/DocumentCenter/View/460 |title = Waterford Township Base Map |scale = Scale not given |location = Waterford Township |publisher = Charter Township of Waterford |url-status = live |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20161220180656/https://waterfordmi.gov/DocumentCenter/View/460 |archive-date = December 20, 2016 |access-date = January 8, 2017 }}</ref><ref>{{cite map |map-url = http://www.historicmapworks.com/Map/US/22335/Waterford+Township/Oakland+County+1908/Michigan/ |map = Waterford Township |title = Standard Atlas of Oakland County Including a Plat Book of the Villages, Cities and Townships of the County |year = 1908 |via =  Historic Map Works |author = Geo. A. Ogle & Co. |scale = 1:31,680 |location = Chicago |publisher = Geo. A. Ogle & Co |url-status = live |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160821054233/http://www.historicmapworks.com/Map/US/22335/Waterford+Township/Oakland+County+1908/Michigan/ |archive-date = August 21, 2016 |access-date = April 29, 2018 }}</ref>\n\nThere are no lakes in Oakland County beginning with the letter X, Y, or Z.\n\n== List ==\n{{incomplete list|date=April 2020}}\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable plainrowheaders\"\n|-\n! scope=\"col\" | Name\n! scope=\"col\" | Location\n! scope=\"col\" | Size (acre)\n! scope=\"col\" | Size (ha)\n! scope=\"col\" | Depth (ft)\n! scope=\"col\" | Depth (m)\n! scope=\"col\" class=\"unsortable\" | Notes\n! scope=\"col\" class=\"unsortable\" | Ref.\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" | Adams Lake\n| [[Orion Township, Michigan|Orion Township]]\n|\n|\n|\n|\n|\n|\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" | Alderman Lake\n| [[Highland Township, Oakland County, Michigan|Highland Township]]\n|\n|\n|\n|\n|\n|\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" | Algoe Lake\n| [[Springfield Township, Oakland County, Michigan|Springfield Township]]\n|\n|\n|\n|\n|\n|\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" | Allen Lake\n| [[Springfield Township, Oakland County, Michigan|Springfield Township]]\n|\n|\n|\n|\n|\n|\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" | Bailey 