es ==\n<references />\n\n[[Category:Lakes of Oakland County, Michigan| ]]\n", "text_old": "{{Use mdy dates|date=April 2020}}\n{{short description|List of lakes}}\n[[File:Cass_Lake_(Michigan)_boats_Wednesdays_(514873849).jpg|right|thumb|350x350px|[[Cass Lake (Michigan)|Cass Lake]], the largest and deepest lake in Oakland County]]There are 387 lakes in Oakland County. Of those lakes, 317 are named while 70 are unnamed lakes.<ref>{{cite web |url = http://www.michigan.gov/dnr/0,1607,7-153-10364_52261_52964_66796-67601--,00.html |title = Oakland County |publisher = Michigan Department of Natural Resources ||url-status = live |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160628034239/http://www.michigan.gov/dnr/0,1607,7-153-10364_52261_52964_66796-67601--,00.html |archive-date = June 28, 2016 |access-date = June 28, 2016 }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url = http://www.lakeplace.com/lakefinder/mi/oakland |title = Oakland County MI Lakes  |work = LakePlace.com |url-status = live |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160305030408/http://www.lakeplace.com/lakefinder/mi/oakland |archive-date = March 5, 2016 |access-date = June 28, 2016 }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url = http://michigan.hometownlocator.com/features/physical,class,lake,scfips,26125,startrow,1.cfm |title = Oakland County Michigan Lakes |work = HometownLocator.com |url-status = live |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160807211257/http://michigan.hometownlocator.com/features/physical,class,lake,scfips,26125,startrow,1.cfm |archive-date = August 7, 2016 |access-date = June 28, 2016 }}</ref><ref>http://www.sportfishjunkies.com/search/lakes--near--rochester-hills-michigan-united-states-of-america</ref><ref>{{google maps |url = https://www.google.com/maps/place/Rose%20Township%20Treasurer%20Office/@42.7204403,-83.6133662,16.75z/data=!4m5!3m4!1s0x0:0x53ab3565e1c47090!8m2!3d42.731769!4d-83.6188579 |title = Rose Township Treasurer Office |access-date = June 28, 2016 }}</ref><ref>{{cite map |author = Charter Township of Waterford |date = January 2014 |url = https://waterfordmi.gov/DocumentCenter/View/460 |title = Waterford Township Base Map |scale = Scale not given |location = Waterford Township |publisher = Charter Township of Waterford |url-status = live |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20161220180656/https://waterfordmi.gov/DocumentCenter/View/460 |archive-date = December 20, 2016 |access-date = January 8, 2017 }}</ref><ref>{{cite map |map-url = http://www.historicmapworks.com/Map/US/22335/Waterford+Township/Oakland+County+1908/Michigan/ |map = Waterford Township |title = Standard Atlas of Oakland County Including a Plat Book of the Villages, Cities and Townships of the County |year = 1908 |via =  Historic Map Works |author = Geo. A. Ogle & Co. |scale = 1:31,680 |location = Chicago |publisher = Geo. A. Ogle & Co |url-status = live |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160821054233/http://www.historicmapworks.com/Map/US/22335/Waterford+Township/Oakland+County+1908/Michigan/ |archive-date = August 21, 2016 |access-date = April 29, 2018 }}</ref>\n\nThere are no lakes in Oakland County beginning with the letter X, Y, or Z.\n\n== List ==\n{{incomplete list|date=April 2020}}\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable plainrowheaders\"\n|-\n! scope=\"col\" | Name\n! scope=\"col\" | Location\n! scope=\"col\" | Size (acre)\n! scope=\"col\" | Size (ha)\n! scope=\"col\" | Depth (ft)\n! scope=\"col\" | Depth (m)\n! scope=\"col\" class=\"unsortable\" | Notes\n! scope=\"col\" class=\"unsortable\" | Ref.\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" | Adams Lake\n| [[Orion Township, Michigan|Orion Township]]\n|\n|\n|\n|\n|\n|\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" | Alderman Lake\n| [[Highland Township, Oakland County, Michigan|Highland Township]]\n|\n|\n|\n|\n|\n|\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" | Algoe Lake\n| [[Springfield Township, Oakland County, Michigan|Springfield Township]]\n|\n|\n|\n|\n|\n|\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" | Allen Lake\n| [[Springfield Township, Oakland County, Michigan|Springfield Township]]\n|\n|\n|\n|\n|\n|\n|-\n! scope